				<div class="comment-body"><p>Shannon:</p>
<p>No, you do not need to be present at any event or be a member of the World Science Fiction Convention to be nominated or to win a Hugo Awards.  The nominations are made by and the final results decided by the members of the annual Worldcon, but anyone can be nominated or win an award.</p>
</div>

