				<div class="comment-body"><p>David:</p>
<p>The Hugo Awards are named after Hugo Gernsback, a seminal figure in the foundation of modern magazine science fiction. See our <a href="../comment-page-1/index.php?page_id=5" rel="nofollow">FAQ</a> for further information.</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
