<p>Your FAQ&#8217;s say that to be considered a book must be &#8220;published&#8221;. Are self-published e-books considered as potential nominees or must the publication be through a traditional publisher? I ask this as I only see novels on your list published through TOR, Del Ray, Orbit, etc. </p>
<p>Can you clairfy?</p>
<p>Thank you for a very well put together and informative web site. </p>
